strategies: I recognized a lot of the cities as capitals so that made recall easier
familiar: If I had heard about it a lot or been there; it got a 5
memorable: If I have heard about memories from a good collection of people; I deemed it memorable
unique: I judged this based off of whether seeing this name pop up on my local news channel would give me pause
realistic: I decided this based off of if I thought the name looked misspelled
